dct_title_s: Map of the Russian possessions in Manchuria to accompany the paper by Revd. W.V. Lloyd
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Russian territorial and district boundaries are shown. Includes inset: Peter the Great or Victoria Bay on an enlarged scale [scale ca. 1:1,763,000]. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 37, (1867), pp. 212-31; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.37 1867
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1867.
